dc_title_s: Rand McNally & Co.'s new street number guide map of Chicago.
dc_description_s: "The index letters and figures on margin of this map correspond with ... Rand McNally & Co.'s Complete City Railway and Street Number Guide to Chicago."   Indexed to railroads.   Summary: Shows the new street numbering system as of 1909, the "L", railroads, elevated roads, and street car lines.|166 x 67 centimeters|Scale [1:158,400]. 2 1/2 inch to 1 mile|City Maps
